\v 10 Kodwa uJesu wathi: Hlalisani abantu phansi. Kwakukhona utshani obunengi ku\add leyo\add*ndawo\x + 6.4. Jow. 2.23.\x*. Ngakho amadoda ahlala phansi inani lawo lalingaba zinkulungwane ezinhlanu\x + Mat. 14.21.\x*.
\v 11 UJesu wasezithatha izinkwa, esebongile wazinika abafundi\x + 6.23. Mat. 15.36.\x*, labafundi kulabo ababehlezi phansi; ngokunjalo lenhlanzana ngangokufuna kwabo\x + 6.11. 21.9,10,13.\x*.
\v 12 Bathi sebesuthi, wathi kubafundi bakhe: Buthani imvuthu eziseleyo, ukuze kungachitheki lutho.
