\v 14 Kwathi lababantu bebona isimangaliso asenzileyo uJesu, bathi: Ngeqiniso lo nguye umProfethi\x + Mat. 21.11,46. Luka 7.16. 9.19. 24.19. Joha. 1.21. 4.19. 7.40. 9.17.\x* omele ukuza emhlabeni\x + 11.27. Mat. 11.3. Mat. 14.33.\x*.
