\v 16 Sekuhlwile, abafundi bakhe behlela elwandle,
\v 17 sebengenile emkhunjini\x + Mat. 14.22,24. Mark. 3.9.\x*, beza ngaphetsheya kolwandle ukuya eKapenawume\x + Mark. 6.45.\x*. Kwasekumnyama, uJesu wayengafikanga kubo.
\v 18 Lwaseluvuka ulwandle ngoba umoya olamandla wawuvunguza.
